    <item>
      <title>波动率期货显示股市恐慌仅限于短期内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/volatility-futures-show-equities-fear-focused-near-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三的强硬信号导致美国股市暴跌，并推动关键波动率指数升至 8 月以来的最高水平，但市场表明这种担忧可能仅限于短期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/volatility-futures-show-equities-fear-focused-near-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:31:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行贝利：利率路径“向下”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/boe-s-bailey-path-of-interest-rates-is-downwards-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利讨论了利率、通胀和英国近期经济数据的前景。在货币政策委员会以 6 比 3 的投票结果维持利率不变之后，他发表了讲话，其中三名官员寻求立即降息。（来源：Pool）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/boe-s-bailey-path-of-interest-rates-is-downwards-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后，美国收益率曲线创 2022 年以来最陡峭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[较长期美国国债周四走弱，推动收益率曲线趋陡至 30 个月前的水平，此前美联储采取了强硬的利率放松政策，并预计明年降息次数将减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果神秘疾病是多种致命疾病的混合体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/mystery-disease-x-in-congo-is-mix-of-illnesses-that-s-turned-deadly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种类似流感的疾病导致刚果民主共和国数百人患病，它是该地区常见的多种疾病的混合体，在因饥饿而虚弱的人群中，这些疾病已经演变成严重的疾病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/mystery-disease-x-in-congo-is-mix-of-illnesses-that-s-turned-deadly</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 13:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
