      <title>美联储刺激比特币价格遭遇 9 月以来最大跌幅，比特币测试 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bitcoin-btc-tests-100-000-after-fed-spurs-worst-drop-since-september</link>
